s show that the scheme has a significantly high detection rate\nwith moderate network traffic overhead and computation overhead in the nodes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Feb 2013 11:43:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-03"}
